name: jupyter_console
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "4.1.1" %}

package:
  name: jupyter_console
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: jupyter_console-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/jupyter/jupyter_console/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: a8b077ae0a5c57e9518ac039ad5febb8

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install

requirements:
  build:
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - jupyter_client
    - ipython
    - ipykernel
    - pexpect  # [not win]
    - pyreadline  # [win]

test:
  commands:
    - jupyter-console -h
  imports:
    - jupyter_console

about:
  home: http://jupyter.org
  license: BSD
  summary: Jupyter terminal console

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - minrk
    - pelson
    - takluyver
